#: ../../run.md:8
msgid "Deploy & Run"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:10
msgid "The Deploy & Run module is for sending transactions to the current **Environment**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:12
msgid "The three main actions of the Deploy & Run module are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:14
msgid "**Deploying** a contract"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:15
msgid "**Accessing** an onchain contract"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:16
msgid "**Interacting** with the functions of a deployed contract"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:18
msgid "This documentation page will cover **Deploying** and **Accessing**. Interacting will be covered in {doc}`Deploy & Run part 2 </udapp>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:20
msgid "![](images/deploy-and-run/a-deploy-run1.png)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:22
msgid "To deploy a contract, you need to have a contract compiled. To check that there is a compiled contract, look in the **CONTRACT** selectbox under the VALUE input field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:24
msgid "If nothing is there, you'll need to compile a contract. If you do not see your desired contract in the CONTRACT selectbox list, make sure the file with the contract is the active tab in the Editor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:26
msgid "Once the contract is selected, choose the chain for deployment and/or method for deployment in the **ENVIRONMENT** selectbox."
