msgid "If you want to connect Remix with a browser wallet (e.g., MetaMask, Phantom), use **Injected Provider**. Select your desired chain in the wallet."
msgstr ""

#: ../../run.md:34
msgid "For assistance with getting the correct configuration (the RPC server address, etc.), click the plug icon next the word **ENVIRONMENT** to go to [chainlist.org](chainlist.org)."
msgstr ""

